column4: NSLOCTEXT("[552C10D5465A93BB276D5FA820A88BD5]", "5E45FF834C519FE3BC309EA983F8806C", "I heard this road is where the bandits attack.")
NSLOCTEXT("[552C10D5465A93BB276D5FA820A88BD5]", "DE09AD414678FB7A7BE8A2BAC21C22BE", "Give up and leave your stuff! Or else!")
NSLOCTEXT("[552C10D5465A93BB276D5FA820A88BD5]", "755675DE43ADAEAB7C899EB096AA4167", "Don\'t worry, we\'re stronger and there\'s more of us. Go get\'um!")
NSLOCTEXT("[552C10D5465A93BB276D5FA820A88BD5]", "814CE5544A3A7060D76ACBA1E0FAEFB4", "Look at them go! They won\'t be back for a while.")
